<section id="arkon-advantage" class="relative py-32 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Indicator -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-10 reveal">
      <span class="font-mono text-[14px] text-forge-amber">06</span>
      <div class="flex-1 dotted-separator"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Heading -->
    <h2 class="font-serif font-normal text-primary-text leading-tight mb-12 reveal" style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.5vw,45px);">
      We don't just build systems. We build the tools that govern them.
    </h2>

    <!-- Body -->
    <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
      <p class="font-sans text-[18px] text-secondary-text leading-relaxed reveal">
        Transformate is the team behind Arkon — an open-source platform used by operators worldwide to monitor, secure, and manage AI systems in production.
      </p>
      <p class="font-sans text-[18px] text-secondary-text leading-relaxed reveal">
        We built Arkon because we needed it ourselves. When you run intelligent systems for clients, you need to know they're working, they're safe, and they're not doing things they shouldn't. Nobody was building that tooling for small teams — so we built it.
      </p>
      <p class="font-sans text-[18px] text-secondary-text leading-relaxed reveal">
        What this means for you: when we build a system inside your business, we bring production-grade discipline. Monitoring. Error handling. Audit trails. The same standards we hold our own infrastructure to.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="reveal">
      <a href="https://github.com/arkon-ai/arkon" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-sans text-forge-amber text-[16px] no-underline hover:text-bright-amber transition-colors duration-200">
